metadata.name: Life #1/33
metadata.description: *Life* is sweet, yet bittersweet, overflowing with abundance, yet bordering on overstimulation. She represents the culmination of today's outpouring of content and culture, resulting in a sickly saccharine mix of various eye-catching features. She is our source of life and inspiration, for which our eyes graze upon her various features, looking for nourishment and meaning. However, upon further inspection, those features seem to melt into nothing.
